      <title>新兴市场动态：债券销售热潮停滞（播客）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/audio/2025-01-19/what-s-happening-in-em-bond-sale-bonanza-stalls-podcast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Selcuk Gokoluk 与 Zijia Song 一起讨论了由于美国借贷成本上升和美联储路径不确定性而导致的新兴市场债券销售停滞。]]></description>
