    <item>
      <title>特朗普的胜利引发了市场的兴奋，现在真正的考验来了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/trump-s-win-sparked-euphoria-in-markets-now-comes-the-real-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在 11 月美国总统大选中获胜，立即引发市场反弹，股市飞涨，美元飙升，比特币价格飙升。但仅仅两个月后，这位共和党人即将重返白宫，而这些交易中只有部分能持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/trump-s-win-sparked-euphoria-in-markets-now-comes-the-real-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 13:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>施纳贝尔告诉 Finanztip，欧洲央行可以降息，但需谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/ecb-can-cut-rates-but-caution-needed-schnabel-tells-finanztip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会成员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔向 Finanztip 表示，随着通胀率向 2% 靠拢，欧洲央行可能还有继续降低借贷成本的空间，但必须谨慎行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/ecb-can-cut-rates-but-caution-needed-schnabel-tells-finanztip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富士电视台因主持人行为调查失去更多广告商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/fuji-tv-loses-more-advertisers-amid-inquiry-into-host-s-behavior</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一名名人主持人被指控行为不当，以及该电视台处理案件的方式受到质疑，日本富士电视台失去了更多广告商，丰田汽车公司也加入了暂停该频道广告的行列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/fuji-tv-loses-more-advertisers-amid-inquiry-into-host-s-behavior</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 08:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行将加息，特朗普允许</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/bank-of-japan-is-set-to-raise-interest-rates-trump-permitting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在加息预期升温且特朗普入主白宫头几天不引发市场冲击的背景下，日本央行行长上田和夫将于周五评估加息的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-18/bank-of-japan-is-set-to-raise-interest-rates-trump-permitting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
